Sonic Runners

   NOTIFICATION OF CLOSURE OF SERVICE

   Run, Jump and Aim for the Top!

What is Sonic Runners?

   An All-New Sonic Action Game is here! Simple controls – just tap to
   jump, dash, and fly! Equip items and buddies to improve your stats and
   run to the top of the leader boards!
     *
     *
     *
     *
     *
     *

Player Characters

   Take control of Sonic and race through every level. BUT, you’ll quickly
   unlock more friends like Tails and Knuckles! Each character has special
   skills that are useful in different stages. Additional characters will
   be added in the future!
   Sonic The Hedgehog

   The Fastest Hedgehog in the World! Sonic is a free spirit with a strong
   sense of right and wrong. He will always rush to the aid of those in
   need.
   Type: Speed/Hero
   Tap the screen while in the middle of a jump to perform a double and
   triple jump.
     *
     *

   Miles 'Tails' Prower

   Tails—real name Miles Prower—is one of Sonic's best pals. He's a
   super-friendly fox cub with two fluffy tails that he can spin at high
   speed to fly through the air.
   Type: Fly/Hero
   Tails is a Fly-type character Tap and hold mid-jump, and he'll float in
   the air.
     *
     *

   Knuckles The Echidna

   Knuckles is a super-strong echidna, and one of Sonic's greatest rivals
   and best friends. A martial arts master, his punches can turn massive
   boulders into dust.
   Type: Power/Hero
   Knuckles is a Power-type character. Tap mid-jump, and he'll launch a
   dash attack.
     *
     *

Buddies

   Sonic and his friends can bring buddies along on their runs! Buddies
   can help boost scores or even enhance item effects. You can match buddy
   types and character types to amplify buddy effects as well! There are
   currently 20 types of Buddies with more to come!

S Rare

   Chip

   Chip
          Perform a final sprint to collect crystals and rings after you
          are defeated.
          Type: Speed

   Caliburn

   Caliburn
          This buddy will automatically attack bosses in boss battles.
          Type: Power

Rare

   yacker

   Yacker
          Extends the duration of color power items.
          Type: Speed

   Golden Pig

   Golden Pig
          Collects and saves rings when players take damage.
          Type: Fly

Normal

   Normal Chao

   Normal Chao
          Adds a bonus to your score.
          Type: Fly

   RC Balloon

   RC Balloon
          Helps to automatically perform big jumps.
          Type: Power

Item

   Players can also equip up to 3 items each run, to help them run to a
   high score!

Equippable Items

   Cyan Laser

   Cyan Laser
          Players temporarily transform into a laser beam. Continuously
          tap the screen to collect rings, crystals, and animals.

   Yellow Drill

   Yellow Drill
          Players temporarily transform into a drill, and burrow
          underground. Tap the screen to jump and collect rings, crystals,
          and animals.

   Indigo Asteroid

   Indigo Asteroid
          Players temporarily transform into an asteroid and fly in the
          air. Tap the screen to float. You can destroy objects and
          collect rings, crystals, and animals.

   Invincible

   Invincible
          Protects players from all damage while the item is active.

Booster Items

   Score Booster

   Score Booster
          Doubles your character bonus score.

   Spring Platforms

   Spring Platforms
          Spring platforms will cover pits to prevent players from
          falling.

